            form.option.painting
              .row.columns(style='margin-bottom: 0;')
                .col.width-75: .info(style='padding: 25px 25px 0;')
                  h1(style='font-size: 24px;') Own A Digital Print
                  p(style='font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px;') Can’t afford an original? Take heart! Save the Storks makes a limited number of digital prints of each piece available as well.
